"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"An internal Pentagon email reportedly outlines options to punish allies over a perceived lack of support for a war with Iran. The document suggests a change in position as a response to the UK not joining the conflict.\",            \"english_title\": \"Pentagon Email on Allies\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un correo del Pent\u00e1gono dice que hay opciones para castigar a aliados por no apoyar una guerra con Ir\u00e1n. El documento sugiere cambiar de posici\u00f3n porque el Reino Unido no se uni\u00f3 al conflicto.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Correo del Pent\u00e1gono sobre Aliados\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The EU's anti-fraud office confirms it has enough information to start an investigation. However, they do not specify if it involves fraud.\",            \"english_title\": \"EU Anti-Fraud Investigation\",            \"translated_version\": \"La oficina anti-fraude de la UE dice que tiene suficiente informaci\u00f3n para empezar una investigaci\u00f3n. Pero no dicen si es sobre fraude.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Investigaci\u00f3n Anti-Fraude de la UE\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Trump's two special envoys will travel to Islamabad on Saturday morning to continue negotiations, according to Press Secretary Karoline Leavitt.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump's Envoys to Islamabad\",            \"translated_version\": \"Dos enviados especiales de Trump viajar\u00e1n a Islamabad el s\u00e1bado por la ma\u00f1ana para seguir negociaciones, seg\u00fan la Secretaria de Prensa Karoline Leavitt.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Enviados de Trump a Islamabad\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Kosovo's court has sentenced two men to life imprisonment and another to a 30-year term for an attack that happened in 2023.\",            \"english_title\": \"Kosovo Court Sentences\",            \"translated_version\": \"El tribunal de Kosovo ha sentenciado a dos hombres a cadena perpetua y a otro a 30 a\u00f1os por un ataque que ocurri\u00f3 en 2023.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Sentencias del Tribunal de Kosovo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Israeli prime minister says he is in excellent physical condition after having a malignant tumor removed.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israeli PM Health Update\",            \"translated_version\": \"El primer ministro de Israel dice que est\u00e1 en excelente condici\u00f3n f\u00edsica despu\u00e9s de que le quitaron un tumor maligno.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Actualizaci\u00f3n de Salud del Primer Ministro de Israel\"        }    ]}"